<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="on-adv">on <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɒn/    美 /ɑːn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在上面：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Make sure the lid is on.
要注意盖上盖子。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>穿着；戴着：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Put your coat on.
把外衣穿上。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>继续地；向前地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We walked on without speaking.
我们默默地向前走。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>(电、水等) 通着；开着：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The light is still on.
灯还亮着。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t leave the tap on.
别让水龙头开着。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.★ <strong>进行中；在上演：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What’s going on?
出什么事了？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What’s on at the movie?
电影院在上演什么片子？</p></div></div>